| **seo-specialist** | GEO Check | `python ~/.claude/skills/geo-fundamentals/scripts/geo_checker.py .` |
| **performance-optimizer** | Lighthouse | `python ~/.claude/skills/performance-profiling/scripts/lighthouse_audit.py <url>` |
